Introduction
‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾
  This package contains 11 new High-Quality Magic-Backgrounds for
  use with Martin Huttenloher's MagicWB. I created @{" 53 backgrounds " SYSTEM "xPlay Cool.snd Q"}
  before - this is the sixth release.

  This time I converted 6 very nice photos to a 16 color palette -
  the first 8 colors are MagicWB, the last 8 colors were defined by
  Roman Patzner (RomIcons). All pictures are 800x600 in size - you
  may crop them to perfectly fit on your screen (and to save RAM).
  These big pictures are in PNG format, because they are half as
  big as equivalent IFF pictures (and even smaller than GIF ;-).

  After all I added 5 standard eight-color textures which can be
  repeated without any visible borders.

@ENDNODE


